## AGH {{ .Version }}

AGH is an agent operating system for running ACP-compatible coding agents as managed sessions.

### Installation

#### Curl Installer
```bash
curl -fsSL https://agh.network/install.sh | sh
```

The installer downloads the release archive for macOS or Linux, verifies it against `checksums.txt`,
installs `agh`, and starts `agh install` when an interactive terminal is available.

#### Binary Download
Download the appropriate `agh_<os>_<arch>.tar.gz` asset for your platform and extract it.

#### Go Install
```bash
go install github.com/pedronauck/agh/cmd/agh@{{ .Tag }}
```
